{"tid":1512613,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】登廣告懸紅緝拿違法疑犯　金額最高$100萬","createTime":"2019-08-28T03:06:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T03:09:48.000Z","uid":307145,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ed1bc2cd4087096cc319357a028992ef5ed9c86b","tid":1512613,"uid":307145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:06:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/22/29/10222949_667540.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F22%2F29%2F10222949_667540.jpg&h=90c5c87c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人登廣告懸紅緝拿多宗案件疑犯。圖：星島<br />\n【橙訊】一個名為「803行動」在多份報章刊登廣告，懸紅緝拿反修例風波至今多宗涉違法及暴力事件的疑犯。據廣告上表示，「803行動」來自社會各界，在8月3日「拋國旗落海事件」後，決定為迄今以來30宗事件懸紅緝拿疑犯，強調所有懸紅賞金均來自民間，日後還會眾籌。<br />\n<br />\n廣告又稱，報料者身份絕對保密，並聲稱有專業團隊負責跟進，以及委託律師向警方報案及提供資料，呼籲市民提供資料。<br />\n<br />\n其中「拋國旗落海」及「塗污中聯辦外國徽」事件，兩宗罪行的懸賞額各達港幣100萬元；而7月1日「噴黑立法會內區徽」和「攻入及破壞立法會」，兩宗個案懸賞額則為港幣50萬元。另外，「721元朗白衣襲擊市民」及「811尖沙咀傷眼事件」懸賞額亦高達40萬元。廣告聲稱，「檢控，就畀錢！」"},{"pid":"187622c232d24fbc251e4094233b5a80532bc71b","tid":1512613,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:06:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ9jU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=5ff7fb41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ9jU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=36f7aeed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F